- Ghost reporters (respond even if closing)

## Close Reason Guidelines

**Use `completed` when:**

- Bug is fixed
- Feature is implemented
- Task is done
- PR merged addressing issue

**Use `not planned` when:**

- Won't implement feature
- Won't fix (works as designed)
- Duplicate (point to original)
- Stale (no activity)
- Cannot reproduce (after investigation)
- Out of scope

